<br />
<br />I don't see any reason why you couldn't make a MMC3 game with PowerPAK &amp; Emulators. If it's good enough to run all these commercial games I don't see how it could be so bad. Maybe the timing isn't perfect but it's close enough for most games. I really can't think of any games that don't work other than the obvious ones without mapper support yet.

		

