<br />
<br />However, I was thinking about <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=5468" class="postlink">that</a> edge case in particular. I wrote a demo that relies on very precise CHR switching timing, I don't know how much I can trust emulators and power pak, that's why it'd always great to have a true SKROM devcard.
<br />
<br />And BTW I should definitely get a power pak soon (I was waiting for a verison with MMC5 support but now it seems I'd just wait forever).

		

